{"tid":1469773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴狗 唔可以入機場","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:09.000Z","uid":98861,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d4eb115d8a7d88d40cca1d36232a37ea8504ce0b","tid":1469773,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仆街與狗不得進入</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記住自有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">保護網</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好出去同佢玩 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n入面有旅遊客  同埋 有order 唔比入機場過橋<br />\n<br />\n狗入場一定恐慌四散<br />\n<br />\n到時冇人再會黎香港旅行<br />\n<br />\n旅遊警示一定提高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得要識退 <br />\n<br />\n正所謂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 彈出彈入 一切小心</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"769e0cbae3da1e790213cc02f08edaf09a7567ca","tid":1469773,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5478d98bb3fd6a0a96bbed86382553ec35970683","tid":1469773,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de80b83a39b413ab41ed6aef0c76dd344e52fb7a","tid":1469773,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:05:08.000Z","msg"